page7.content: | CSSE | CSP | CSA | Game | . . . Investing in your Technical Future . Explore the Computer Science Pathway at Del Norte High School. All Del Norte CompSci classes are designed to provide a real-world development experience. Grading is focused on time invested, analytics, participation with peers, and engagement in learning. . Project-based learning with teacher support | Tech Talks by teacher complimented with Student Teaching | Course learning includes Coding Languages, DevOps, GitHub, Research and Ceativity | Student teams practice Agile Development Methodologies: planning, communication, collaboration | Class lab time provided and approximately 2-3 hours of homework per week | .
